{"word":"G5619 - ὡσπερεί - hōspereí - hoce-per-i' - As","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὡσπερεί</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hōspereí</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoce-per-i'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">As</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"போன்ற - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"as, as it were"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5618 - ὥσπερ - hṓsper - hoce'-per/5618\">G5618</a> and <a href=\"#/G1487 - εἰ - ei - i/1487\">G1487</a>; <i>just as if</i>, that is, <i>as it were:</i> - as.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}